<a href="http://www.caadp.net/news/?p=768" target="_self">http://www.caadp.net/news/?p=768</a></p><p>COMESA, press release, ‘Kenya signs CAADP: launches agricultural sector development strategy’, undated</p><p>
<a href="http://www.comesa.int/lang-en/component/content/article/34-general-news/493--kenya-signs-caadp-launches-agricultural-sector-development-strategy" target="_self">http://www.comesa.int/lang-en/component/content/article/34-general-news/...</a></p><p>COMESA, Uganda CAADP Compact, 31 March 2010</p><p>
